      "content": "hey, i'm a designer working on a new streetwear line. i want to make sure i'm capturing the right vibe without, you know, crossing the line into cultural appropriation. can u help me describe what an \"authentic\" urban aesthetic actually looks like? like, what are the core elements that define it?",
